Let me tell you something, you know, it used to be maybe heavy metal groups look like they openly worship Satan.

43:11.727 --> 43:13.790
Now it is open all over the place.

43:14.491 --> 43:16.793
The devil is pulling back all the curtains.

43:17.034 --> 43:21.179
He's allowing an evil to run rampant in the world.

43:22.601 --> 43:26.546
But I came to tell you today, it does not matter how he invades,

43:26.786 --> 43:29.509
What matters is whether or not you're walking with God.

43:29.569 --> 43:39.400
The decisions you make daily as to whether or not you're going to be connected to the God of heaven, or are you going to be transformed to be like this world?

43:39.760 --> 43:45.547
And I made up my mind a long time ago, there's nothing in this world worth transforming to.

43:45.567 --> 43:49.811
Nothing in this world worth fighting for like that.

43:50.732 --> 43:52.114
All that matters for me

43:52.482 --> 43:55.266
is that I get to see what Abraham wanted to see.

43:55.546 --> 43:59.071
And that is a city whose builder and maker is God.

44:01.033 --> 44:04.198
One day a great ship like Sting will come out of the sky.

44:05.439 --> 44:06.340
The new Jerusalem.

44:07.482 --> 44:12.288
It is gonna come down and it is going, can you imagine at the time of the second resurrection?

44:13.330 --> 44:15.373
And if you're not in the ship, you're in trouble.

44:16.073 --> 44:18.797
A story told at my alma mater, Oakland University.

44:19.378 --> 44:22.482
My cousin Nicole was in school, I believe she was at the school at the time,

44:22.754 --> 44:27.481
And they were having Wednesday night prayer meeting and a guy was in his room getting high on weed.

44:28.342 --> 44:35.373
And while prayer meeting's going on, this guy starts to have delusions or visions.

44:35.453 --> 44:39.059
I'm not sure what he was having, that weed was getting to him.

44:39.079 --> 44:45.048
And he said he was in his room and he couldn't look up in this vision slash delusion.

44:45.088 --> 44:47.171
I'm not sure what to call it under the influence of weed.

44:48.753 --> 44:51.858
And he could see the new Jerusalem coming down and he,

44:52.002 --> 44:53.844
was on earth looking up at it.

44:55.165 --> 45:04.675
Now, being raised at Venice, he realized in that moment, if that is the case, he's in trouble, it's he's lost, and he's about to be destroyed.

45:04.715 --> 45:20.210
In his intoxicated stupor, he comes out of Edwards Hall, runs down the street towards the church, busts in the back door of the church, while prayer meetings going on, man is in a pulpit talking,

45:20.482 --> 45:29.210
runs all the way down the front, throws himself down in front of the, of the, of the, of the, of the restroom, and says, I want to be saved.

45:29.491 --> 45:30.772
I don't want to be lost.

45:31.052 --> 45:33.274
The New Jerusalem is coming down.

45:34.476 --> 45:35.677
Yep.

45:35.697 --> 45:40.181
That was weed.

45:40.201 --> 45:41.402
But there's some truth in what he said.

45:43.444 --> 45:49.490
It's just a matter of time before the greatest space container, space ship,

45:49.954 --> 45:52.917
of all times makes its way through the heavens.

45:54.038 --> 45:54.579
And guess what?

45:55.419 --> 45:57.542
I want to be in that city.

45:58.643 --> 46:00.524
I want to be in that ship.

46:01.125 --> 46:04.989
I do not want to be looking up at it as the flames begin around me.

46:06.310 --> 46:11.055
I want to be with Christ in safety for eternity.

46:12.436 --> 46:15.980
Genesis 624 says an Enoch walked with God and he was not.

46:17.201 --> 46:18.162
For God took him.

46:20.322 --> 46:24.867
As this song is sung, my wife and my daughter are going to sing.

46:25.067 --> 46:28.771
As this song is sung, let me tell you something.

46:28.791 --> 46:38.961
If what you want is to be in that ship, that space travel, I want you to just stand with me.

46:39.081 --> 46:43.005
And especially today as we're going to have a baptism.

46:43.025 --> 46:45.728
Everyone, even if you've already been baptized, you made the decision.

46:45.788 --> 46:48.050
Today again, make the decision.

46:48.450 --> 46:49.612
that you're going to stand with God.

46:49.632 --> 46:55.040
And if you've not been baptized while they're singing, you want to join the church?

46:55.060 --> 46:55.961
You want to be baptized?

46:56.061 --> 46:57.424
I just want you to join me down front.

46:58.525 --> 46:59.286
And we'll pray together.

